The paper deals with loss bounds for prediction learning and games, which are topics commonly studied in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves information theory and data structures, which suggests cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as possible sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses game theory, which could place it in cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
